1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"咁全香港邊個唔死 抵啦咁 <br />\n陷港剷囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"大把淡友部署緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"有1球野既人唔會做淡友 等淡<br />\n1球野都冇 到時真係跌9成，妳都冇按揭做<br />\nbtw 跌9成 6百萬樓 跌到60萬 1球野都買唔到2間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我角度啦，黎緊會長期疲軟，但冇大新聞，唔會暴跌啦。仲要中國qe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,打完貿易戰就有暗湧升市。"},{"pid":"6850cce1854ec156019047e89e24f04edcd06c4e","tid":756819,"uid":191900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"蘋果真係好燈 信佢真係死得"},{"pid":"570f93752a90e8b15c9b5ba52cad4a6df4f2c9ce","tid":756819,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"颳風又燈<br />\n樓市又燈<br />\n最撚燈係香港民主"},{"pid":"2e465598e670434cb5496126f777d4150045c645","tid":756819,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6850cce1854ec156019047e89e24f04edcd06c4e","tid":756819,"uid":191900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"蘋果真係好燈 信佢真係死得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"支那好 香港更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}